data.description: Welcome to your new coastal retreat! This charming home boasts 3 bedrooms, 1 bath, a spacious front porch and has undergone a renovation with an updated bathroom, brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring, fresh carpet and paint throughout. Situated just 2 blocks from the beach and golf course, this home offers the perfect blend of coastal living and recreation. Access to local amenities, shops, and dining options, ensuring a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.
